node.text:
Link in bio to explore my squat programs 😤🦾

🔹Level 1: 5 week building program. VOLUME! 3x a week frequency. Back squats. Build muscle and work on technique. Accessory work focused on hamstrings.

🔹Level 2: 8 week building program. 2x a week frequency. Adding in front squats with back squats. You will be alternating between heavier and lighter weeks. Accessory work to strengthen weaknesses.

🔹Level 3: 6 week peaking program. 3x a week frequency. Front and back squats. Accessory work to strengthen weaknesses. Higher %

LFG! #strongissexy
Gettin back into front squatz 🏋️‍♀️Super light but will build up over time 🙌 I had a killer session tonight! I LOVE to train🦾
